{
  "message": "Add missing starlight-llms-txt dependencies for bun\n\nWhen installing from a GitHub monorepo, bun doesn't automatically\ninstall the nested package's dependencies. Add them explicitly to\npackage.json. Grouped at the end for easy removal once we switch\nto the official release.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
